String.string: Tree of Ancient Gods
Under the Tree of Ancient Gods
Jovin is with a small group working on something under the World Tree.
Go to the base of the World Tree.
"How does it work?"
Talk to Jovin.
Activate the Armillariscope.
"If I identify the culprit, you'll be the first person I notify."
Talk to Jovin again.
Inside of the Base
Federation soldiers are recovering the bodies of the dead.
Search Tower Base for clues.
"One person, working alone. Got it. Thanks."
Talk to the federation investigator.
Inside of the Base
Researchers are investigating the imprints from the Tree.
Search Tower Base for more clues.
"That fits with what else I've been able to learn. Thank you."
Talk to the federation investigator.
Inside of the Base
There is a body in the weeds.
Continue searching Tower Base for clues.
"This...looks familiar."
Examine the body of federation soldier.
"I think I know this man. Thanks. I'll keep an eye out for him."
Talk to the soldier.
"You can count on me."
Report to Adria in Ruined Temple.
